<hr>
<strong>WORKS CITED</strong>
<br>
<br>
Add a &#8216;Works Cited&#8217; entry at the end of your essay citing all sources used in the body of your writing.
<br><br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br>
<blockquote>
	<div class="ref-hang-indent">Author&#8217;s Name. <em>Title of Book</em>. 
		Publisher, year of publication. 
	</div>
	<div class="ref-hang-indent">
		&#45;&nbsp;&#45;&nbsp;&#45;. <em>Title of Book</em>. Publisher, year of publication. 
	</div>
</blockquote>
<br>
Give the author&#8217;s name in the first entry only. After that use three hyphens, followed by a full stop to indicate the author name is exactly the same. List works alphabetically by title.
<br><br>
References with the same first author and a different second or third author are listed alphabetically by name.
<br><br>
<strong>Example</strong>
<br>
If the publisher is an academic press, replace <em>Press</em> with <em>P</em>. For further information on publisher abbreviations, see 1.6.3 in the <a href="http://west-sydney-primo.hosted.exlibrisgroup.com/UWS-ALMA:default_scope:UWS-ALMA21186157620001571" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MLA Handbook (8th edition)</a>.	
<br>
<blockquote>
	<div class="ref-hang-indent">
		<span class="hover" title="Author&#8217;s Name">Smith, Andrea</span>. 
		<em><span class="hover" title="Title of Book">Amid Fifty Thousand Flaming Devils</span></em>. 
		<span class="hover" title="Publisher">Etoile P</span>, 
		<span class="hover" title="year of publication">2056</span>.
	</div>
	<div class="ref-hang-indent">
		<span class="hover" title="Author&#8217;s Name">&#45;&nbsp;&#45;&nbsp;&#45;</span>. 
		<em><span class="hover" title="Title of Book">Exploring Nanoscale Science</span></em>. 
		<span class="hover" title="Publisher">Beck</span>, 
		<span class="hover" title="year of publication">2050</span>. 
	</div>
	<div class="ref-hang-indent">
		<span class="hover" title="Author&#8217;s Name">Smith, Andrea, and Beryl Brown</span>. 
		<em><span class="hover" title="Title of Book">Exploring New Frontiers</span></em>. 
		<span class="hover" title="Publisher">Beck</span>, 
		<span class="hover" title="year of publication">2056</span>.
	</div>
</blockquote>
